## 4. Case Study Example (Rebel Coffee)

Monday — chaos in positioning.  
Sunday — new brand.

Before: 12 logo options. None worked.  
After: one. It works.

+187 % site traffic in first 30 days.  
Revisions: 1.

“And they saw that it was good.”  
— Founder, Rebel Coffee

